                <h3>Edit in your browser with our online PDF editor</h3>
                <p>Open the online PDF editor with Safari or your other favourite browser.</p>
              </li>

              <li>
                <h3>Edit with our offline Mac PDF editor app</h3>
                <p>
                  Download and install Sejda Desktop for Mac and edit your PDF files offline.<br>
                  <a href="./desktop">Sejda Desktop</a>
                </p>
              </li>
            </ol>
